      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. Mechanically, it runs smoothly with a strong engine and responsive transmission, having recently passed a full safety inspection. The exterior looks great overall, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and some light surface scratches consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster and all electronics functioning as intended. It is a reliable, solid choice for anyone looking for a quality vehicle that is ready to drive immediately.",
